        "date": "2026-04-07T10:35:37Z",
        "message": "feat(backend): add automatic model redownload on corruption\n\n- Implement automatic re-download of corrupted models from HuggingFace\n  and ModelScope when OSError occurs during model loading\n- Add support for local path mode with appropriate error handling\n  since local paths cannot be automatically re-downloaded\n- Wrap re-download logic in nested exception handling to catch\n  different failure scenarios\n- Change log level from error to warning for initial corruption\n  detection to reduce noise\n\nfeat(backend): add token counting functionality\n\n- Implement count_tokens method to calculate token numbers using\n  the model's processor\n- Add proper validation to check if model is loaded before counting\n- Include detailed logging for debugging token calculation results\n\nfeat(frontend): add real-time token counter to UI\n\n- Create update_token_counter function to calculate and format\n  token counts for display\n- Add HTML elements to show token counts in generation, design\n  and clone tabs\n- Implement live updates that trigger on text input changes\n- Handle edge cases like empty text and unloaded models with\n  appropriate messages\n\nstyle(main): add CSS styling for token counter display\n\n- Add CSS rules for token counter elements to improve visual\n  appearance\n- Style counters with monospace font, background color and\n  rounded corners\n\nchore(version): bump version to 0.0.4",
        "url": "https://github.com/licyk/qwen-tts-webui/commit/9ef10824ac7a454c447c9afdda3e0008435ab0d0"
    },
